u i BC-FALUN-GONG-REVIEW-2ND     04-29 0955
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FALUN-GONG-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 SHANGHAI, China: in public.  
<TEXT>
