   BOTTOM
</P>
<P>
   HIGHSCHOOL-GAY-ATHLETE (Middleton, Mass.) _ For Corey Johnson, a
gay high school football captain who ``came out'' and announced his
homosexuality, the response of his teammates and his school
community was illuminating. By Robert Lipsyte.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 1 p.m. ET in ``s'' news file.)
