</P>
<P>
   BIGBUCK-MOVIES (Los Angeles) _ The summer season arrives next
weekend with the debut of ``Gladiator,'' the first in a legion of
blockbuster pictures, many of them animated and effects-filled
extravaganzas, that will march into theaters weekend after weekend
through Labor Day. By David Bloom. (Will move in the ``a'' national
news file and in the ``n'' California news files.)
</P>
<P>
   LA-STREETS (Los Angeles) _ The streets of Los Angeles -
neglected for decades - are still crumbling faster than they are
being repaired, despite a massive increase in spending under Mayor
Richard Riordan. Despite the mayor's proposal to launch the city's
largest-ever street repair program, Los Angeles still lags woefully
behind in patching thousands of miles of broken blacktop. By Alexa
Haussler. (Will move in the ``n'' California news file.)
</P>
