<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Haunted by his homies
 &HT;    By Mike Fish and Dan Chapman
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ The party is kicking this night as Luther Campbell of
