   He has the money: $2,000 in cash that guys eagerly hand over to
entice the ladies to get wild.
</P>
<P>
   He has the talent: a handful of buxom, skimpily clad young women
willing to perform sexual acts for the prize money.
</P>
<P>
   He has the celebrities: ``Ladies and gentlemen _ Ray Lewis,''
Campbell announces on the 1999 video.
</P>
<P>
   Lewis, the Baltimore Ravens star linebacker, enters Coco Bongo
